	(text "Power: UBEC ~5V IN -> PTC fuse -> P-MOSFET reverse-polarity protect -> VSYS\nVSYS feeds DevKitC-1 5V pin directly (esp32.kicad_sch).\nTPS563201 buck gives E22 its OWN ~5.07V rail (E22_VCC), isolated from VSYS\nso E22's 500-650mA TX current pulses cannot brown-out the ESP32." (at 12.7 15.24 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5))) (uuid "7e461355-b170-468e-b51b-58b64b80531e"))
